00029 CHPMultiDataFileWriter::CHPMultiDataFileWriter(CHPMultiDataData &p)
00030 {
00031         data = &p;
00032         map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo> &info = p.GetDataSetInfo();
00033         map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo>::iterator it;
00034         for (it=info.begin(); it!=info.end(); it++)
00035         {
00036                 dataTypeToIndex[it->first] = it->second.dataSetIndex;
00037                 indexToDataType[it->second.dataSetIndex] = it->first;
00038         }
00039         writer = new GenericFileWriter(p.GetFileHeader());
00040         WriteHeaders();
00041 }

00049 void CHPMultiDataFileWriter::WriteHeaders()
00050 {
00051         writer->WriteHeader();
00052     int ng = writer->GetDataGroupCnt();
00053     for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
00054     {
00055             DataGroupWriter &dataGroupWriter = writer->GetDataGroupWriter(ig);
00056             dataGroupWriter.WriteHeader();
00057 
00058             int32_t n = dataGroupWriter.GetDataSetWriterCnt();
00059             for (int32_t i=0; i<n; i++)
00060             {
00061                     dataSetWriter = &dataGroupWriter.GetDataSetWriter(i);
00062                     dataSetWriter->WriteHeader();
00063                     entryPos[indexToDataType[i]] = SetFilePositions();
00064                     dataGroupWriter.UpdateNextDataGroupPos();
00065             }
00066     }
00067 }

00069 int32_t CHPMultiDataFileWriter::SetFilePositions()
00070 {
00071         int32_t dataSetSz = dataSetWriter->GetDataSetSize();
00072         int32_t offset = writer->GetFilePos();
00073         writer->SeekFromCurrentPos(dataSetSz + 1);
00074         dataSetWriter->UpdateNextDataSetOffset();
00075         return offset;
00076 }

00078 void CHPMultiDataFileWriter::SeekToDataSet(MultiDataType dataType)
00079 {
00080     int ig = data->GetDataGroupIndex(dataType);
00081     DataGroupWriter &dataGroupWriter = writer->GetDataGroupWriter(ig);
00082     writer->SeekFromBeginPos(entryPos[dataType]);
00083     dataSetWriter = &dataGroupWriter.GetDataSetWriter(dataTypeToIndex[dataType]);
00084     maxName = data->GetMaxProbeSetName(dataType);
00085     if (dataType == FamilialSegmentOverlapsMultiDataType)
00086     {
00087         std::map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo> &dinfo = data->GetDataSetInfo();
00088         maxSegmentType = dinfo[dataType].maxSegmentType;
00089         maxReferenceSegmentID = dinfo[dataType].maxReferenceSegmentID;
00090         maxFamilialSegmentID = dinfo[dataType].maxFamilialSegmentID;
00091     }
00092     else if (dataType == FamilialSamplesMultiDataType)
00093     {
00094         std::map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo> &dinfo = data->GetDataSetInfo();
00095         maxFamilialARRID = dinfo[dataType].maxFamilialARRID;
00096         maxFamilialCHPID = dinfo[dataType].maxFamilialCHPID;
00097         maxFamilialCHPFile = dinfo[dataType].maxFamilialCHPFile;
00098         maxFamilialRole = dinfo[dataType].maxFamilialRole;
00099     }
00100     currentDataType = dataType;
00101 }

00300 void CHPMultiDataFileWriter::WriteMetrics(const std::vector<affymetrix_calvin_parameter::ParameterNameValueType> &metrics)
00301 {
00302         int ncols = (int) metrics.size();
00303         for (int icol=0; icol<ncols; icol++)
00304         {
00305                 const ParameterNameValueType &nv = metrics[icol];
00306                 switch (nv.GetParameterType())
00307                 {
00308                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int8Type:
00309                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueInt8());
00310                         break;
00311 
00312                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt8Type:
00313                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueUInt8());
00314                         break;
00315 
00316                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int16Type:
00317                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueInt16());
00318                         break;
00319 
00320                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type:
00321                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueUInt16());
00322                         break;
00323 
00324                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type:
00325                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueInt32());
00326                         break;
00327 
00328                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt32Type:
00329                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueUInt32());
00330                         break;
00331 
00332                 case ParameterNameValueType::FloatType:
00333                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueFloat());
00334                         break;
00335 
00336                 case ParameterNameValueType::AsciiType:
00337                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueAscii(), data->GetMetricColumnLength(currentDataType, icol));
00338                         break;
00339 
00340                 case ParameterNameValueType::TextType:
00341                         dataSetWriter->Write(nv.GetValueText(), data->GetMetricColumnLength(currentDataType, icol));
00342                         break;
00343                         // @todo check this is ok.
00344                 case ParameterNameValueType::UnknownType:
00345                         break;
00346                 }
00347         }
00348 }
